  "text": "Successfully completed comprehensive documentation update for Provider terminology migration:\n\n✅ Updated docs/project/LANGUAGE.md:\n- Changed all \"Destination\" to \"Provider\" in terminology table\n- Updated system variables from $destination to $provider\n- Updated all examples and delimiter usage\n- Added comprehensive migration section with timelines\n- Added backwards compatibility notes\n- Updated changelog with breaking change notice\n\n✅ Updated CLAUDE.md:\n- Updated overview to use \"provider-specific\" terminology\n- Changed Destination section to Provider section\n- Updated variable examples\n- Updated frontmatter examples\n- Updated scoped properties terminology\n\n✅ Updated README.md:\n- Changed overview description to providers\n- Updated all core concept definitions\n- Changed \"Supported Destinations\" to \"Supported Providers\"\n- Updated configuration examples\n- Updated variable reference table\n\n✅ Updated packages/types/MIGRATION.md:\n- Added Provider terminology migration section at top\n- Updated all code examples to use new interfaces\n- Changed DestinationPlugin → RulesetProvider\n- Updated all variable names throughout examples\n\nThe documentation now accurately reflects the completed Provider terminology refactoring. All user-facing documentation is consistent and includes clear migration guidance.",
